item.title: Treasury Yields Rise on Jobs Data, Fall on GDP
item.description: Treasury yields wobbled, getting a boost after a hotter-than-expected ADP jobs report and then losing steam after weaker-than-expected U.S. GDP data.

item.description: Sales of newly built homes have been on a tear. But builders are likely to soon face stiffer competition for buyers.

item.title: Alphabet shares rise on earnings beats boosted by cloud revenue
item.description: Google parent Alphabet reported third-quarter earnings that beat on top and bottom lines.

item.title: Dow Futures Edge Down; Alphabet Shares Rally
item.description: Dow industrials futures crept lower, weighed down by a post-earnings decline in Caterpillar stock. S&P 500 and Nasdaq-100 futures were little changed.
